ography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"editor\":\"<p>Seen above: The icons.\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"cff3e1e\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6d6fce9\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a5cd5cf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"wp_gallery\":[{\"id\":74,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/Artboard-3.png\"},{\"id\":75,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/dogpatternblue.png\"}],\"thumbnail_size\":\"medium_large\",\"gallery_columns\":\"2\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-gallery\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"82ca8e9\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a823223\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ba9c2c3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>The patterns that I created for True Blue are very simple and whimsical line drawings of dogs, cats, bones, toy balls and leaves. These patterns are to be used on certain packaging and collateral branding elements. The colours used in these patterns stay true to the colour palette chosen for the company and ties in their love of animals with the fun animal prints.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"570bffb\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"928b00e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b1ead81\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"space\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":25}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"},{\"id\":\"1689837\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Stationery\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"3cd6435\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d03f8d0\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8d65727\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/Colorful-Business-Card-MockUp.png\",\"id\":77}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a0f229f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3423321\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"914359a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-family: AvenirNext; font-size: 12pt;\\\">Because of the simple and modern look of the branding, I want the stationery to accent the whimsical and playful side of the True Blue company. All of the stationery will be printed on recycled paper to keep the business sustainable and eco-friendly.<br \\/><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: AvenirNext;\\\">The business cards will be bright and fun. There are two versions of the chosen design: the fi<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: AvenirNext;\\\">rst has the top of the business card as the brand\\u2019s yellow colour with the white paw print logo and <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: AvenirNext;\\\">the back of the card has the darker blue colour with the information in the off-white ivory colour; the second version has the green colour with the \\u201cTrue\\u201d [paw-print] \\u201cBlue\\u201d logo as the top of the business card and the lighter blue colour on the back side with the information. The business cards will be printed on a recycled cold-pressed watercolour paper that is thick (350-400 GSM), matte and textured.\\u00a0<br \\/><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: AvenirNext; font-size: 12pt;\\\">The letterhead will be printed on a recycled A4 paper that is 80 GSM. The paper will be the off-white ivory colour chosen for the brand. There will be the company\\u2019s icon printed on the page like a watermark so that writing on top of it will be easily legible. True Blue\\u2019s primary logo will be centred at the top of the page, while the company\\u2019s information will be posted along the bottom of the page under a line that is the darker blue company colour. The font used on the letterheads will be Shree Devanagari 714, as it is a more familiar font and is easier to read as a big block of text.\\u00a0<br \\/><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: AvenirNext;\\\">The envelopes will be a standard #9 or #10 basic white recycled envelope that is 90-100 GSM to hold up during shipping. On the back of the envelope, the \\u201cTrue\\u201d [paw-print] \\u201cBlue\\u201d logo <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: AvenirNext;\\\">will be centred just under the flap that seals the envelope. The flap will have the paw print pattern design on the outside, and the inside of the flap will have the company\\u2019s main logo colour which is <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: AvenirNext;\\\">the darker blue.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"76c3dd0\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fffddd2\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7729ac3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"space\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":25}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"},{\"id\":\"08e0a4e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{