"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7477291\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"93920b4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"editor\":\"<p>We were asked to choose a local company and rebrand them. We needed to change or update the logo, the stationery, the packaging and all of the marketing strategies. I chose True Blue Pet Supplies located in Campbell River, B.C. As shown above, their logo needed an update and a bump into the 21st century.\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"52adcea\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e1c6828\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fed553f\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"space\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":25}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"},{\"id\":\"b7aadb3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"The New Logo\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"7312998\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/Artboard-1.png\",\"id\":69},\"image_size\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8fced17\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"523cd47\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8c2f258\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"editor\":\"<p>The logo that I created for True Blue Pet Supplies is a clean, modern, circular design. The round, organic design reflects the organic nature of Vancouver Island and True Blue as a company. The fact that their products are all natural is complimented by the natural feel of this logo design.<br \\/><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">The main pop of colour I chose for the logo is a natural blue-green colour that provides the bright element of visual interest. This tone of blue is calm and breezy, while making the logo easy to read on stationery, invoices, etc. This colour is much more modern and clean than the stark \\\"Windows Paint Program\\\" shade of blue that was originally used.<\\/span><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"37442a2\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"757919b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"cb6ac6e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"space\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":25}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"},{\"id\":\"9be5f89\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Logo Variations &amp; Patterns\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"260cd08\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"wp_gallery\":[{\"id\":72,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/Artboard-6.png\"},{\"id\":70,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/Artboard-2.png\"},{\"id\":71,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/Artboard-5.png\"}],\"thumbnail_size\":\"large\",\"gallery_columns\":\"3\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-gallery\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c754cca\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d598132\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"de3f503\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typog