nt roller on a free stock-image website. I came up with the message \\\"Come. Create. Caffeinate.\\\" as a simple but effective message to explain what Espress Yourself offers. I added the coffee ring at the bottom because I felt as though the paint roller was not sending the full message visually.\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"dc60143\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"74c7b12\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"031c7ad\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Landing Page\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"456a74c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"808a83d\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"0a5cd45\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/SMALLPAGE.png\",\"id\":136},\"image_size\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"5c41aaa\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"20afad3\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a59f45c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"editor\":\"<p>This landing page for Espress Yourself was designed to motivate the customer to submit their email address and sign up to book their wall space to create on. I wanted to keep the design minimal with a lot of white space. I used images revolving around paint and coffee to keep the landing page on brand. I used the dark brown and bright purple colours for consistency. This landing page consists of a form at the top, the benefits and features section, the testimonial section, and a second call to action at the bottom along with the logo and social media links.\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
