(1106, 236, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"9d122f8\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"db8b3b6\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6c4b365\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/IMG_3721.jpg\",\"id\":146}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"977d44d\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a1581d5\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6b55067\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Alyssa Willis\",\"title_color\":\"#a48179\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"700\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"0a770d9\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c8d241e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2da64b4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"editor\":\"<p>Hi! My name is Alyssa. Pronounced uh-li-ss-uh. Not Alysha. Not Melissa. Sometimes you can get away with calling me Aly. But my name is Alyssa. Last name, Willis. I have heard so many \\\"What you talkin\' \'bout Willis\\\" jokes in my life, I will not laugh if you attempt it. Stop that. Get some help.<\\/p><p>I am a student at North Island College in Comox Valley studying in the Communication Design Program. Since I was a child, I have had a love for art and computers. I first explored my love of art through the basic paint and pens. Later on in life, I became a certified Nail Technician. I find my Nail Technician training really helped me with my art skills, my colour theory and my tactful and caring nature with clients.<\\/p><p>Since enrolling in the Communication Design Program, I feel as though I have found my calling in life. And although I am still learning, I am so proud of my skill set thus far.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>I am a lifelong and <strong><em>die-hard<\\/em><\\/strong>\\u00a0Disney\\/Pixar fan. I am the reigning champ of \\\"Name That Tune: Disney Edition\\\" in my family\\/friend group. I carry that title with pride. I worked hard for that, man.<\\/p><p>My other interests include: Vines and Vine references, Youtube, photography, Starbucks, comedy and horror\\/thriller movies, the vastness of space, conspiracy theories, Reddit, nail art, 90\'s cartoons and movies, thrift shopping, and cats. Especially my fur baby, Mew. And Wilfred Warrior on Instagram.<\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c86a466\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"cd8ec92\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ab2fd09\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Skill Set\",\"header_size\":\"h3\",\"title_color\":\"#a48179\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"11e8279\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"222be5e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"52dc49b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"unmarked_star_style\":\"outline\",\"title\":\"ILLUSTRATOR\",\"title_color\":\"#a48179\",\"title_typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"title_typography_font_family\":\"Libre Franklin\",\"title_typography_font_weight\":\"800\",\"stars_color\":\"#a48179\",\"stars_unmarked_color\":\"#a48179\",\"_animation\":\"fadeIn\",\"_css_classes\":\"star\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"star-rating\"},{\"id\":\"ccb2b25\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"unmar