ked hard for that, man.<\\/p><p>My other interests include: Vines and Vine references, Youtube, photography, Starbucks, comedy and horror\\/thriller movies, the vastness of space, conspiracy theories, Reddit, nail art, 90\'s cartoons and movies, thrift shopping, and cats. Especially my fur baby, Mew. And Wilfred Warrior on Instagram.<\\/p><p>I hope to travel one day, and have a list of places that I would love to explore, including: Disneyland (again), Peru, Scotland and the Philippines.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>I am almost always smiling and laughing, or finding a way to make others smile and laugh because I think that is what life is all about. In the end, it\'s about the memories we make.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>I would love to help people create their brand, develop their brand\'s personality and bring it to life. If you are in the process of getting your brand on it\'s feet, I would love to help enable you to express yourself.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c86a466\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"cd8ec92\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ab2fd09\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Skill Set\",\"header_size\":\"h3\",\"title_color\":\"#a48179\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"11e8279\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"222be5e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"52dc49b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"unmarked_star_style\":\"outline\",\"title\":\"ILLUSTRATOR\",\"title_color\":\"#a48179\",\"title_typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"title_typography_font_family\":\"Libre Franklin\",\"title_typography_font_weight\":\"800\",\"stars_color\":\"#a48179\",\"stars_unmarked_c