(1170, 250, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"30cdbb7\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b780a1d\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"037624d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Personal Logo\",\"title_color\":\"#a48179\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"700\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1879427c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b95864a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"351c252c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Since I was young, I have loved art, computers and space. I am enthralled by the way a brush and some colour can change the look and feel of something. I am astounded by the way you can create something from your mind with a little imagination and some supplies. I have been using a computer since the age of 5 and within a few months, I was teaching my parents how to do things on the computer. And I am completely taken aback by the vastness of space, and imagining what could be out there.<\\/p><p>So, with all these things in mind, a graphic designer seemed like the career that contained the perfect combination of my favourite things and my skill sets. But, where could I introduce some space vibes? Of course, every client wouldn\'t want NASA type logos or galaxy watercolored backgrounds and all that stuff.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>I decided that for my personal logo - I would create a nerdy, spacey, astronaut feel.\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Why not? It\'s my logo!<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a88138d\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"47f8e64\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"70555a3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"The Logo\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"dcf5532\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/black.png\",\"id\":105},\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"be05a77\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"23e1d26\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a3cd6e3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"editor\":\"<p>This is the basic logo. The logo that would be seen most of the time - you know, when some would say it\'s \\\"inappropriate\\\" to have a bright pink logo present. Which is strange... Because pink is a fantastically happy colour.<\\/p><p>I created this logo by finding a NASA-like font and making use of it to reflect me! I brought the letters A and W (no, not like the burgers, but yum!) into Illustrator and modified them until they melded into one another.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>It\'s funny, it kind of looks the way I sign my initials.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"672cbfe\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Logo Variations\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"989a887\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"40\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9acdd4f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2a96535\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/blue.png\",\"id\":109},\"image_size\":\"full\",\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"40a5cdc\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"50c1878\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/yellow.png\",\"id\":119},\"image_size\":\"full\",\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"3564583\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2f3db61\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/pink.png\",\"id\":114},\"image_size\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d3acc2b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d5ff694\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/green.png\",\"id\":111},\"image_size\":\"full\",\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1bb1272\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"40\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"42c71cd\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4952a11\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/blueoutline.png\",\"id\":110},\"image_size\":\"full\",\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"ed97228\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3b6cb61\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/yellowoutline.png\",\"id\":120},\"image_size\":\"full\",\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"383f410\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f04b66e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/pinkoutline.png\",\"id\":115},\"image_size\":\"full\",\"link_to\":\"file\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"987f6ea\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3b004e7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/greenoutline.png\",\"id\":112},\"image_size\":\"full\",\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8dff1a2\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d2949ca\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5d55d77\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>These are all the variations of my personal logo. There is not much difference from the basic logo - but I have always been drawn to bright and vibrant colour. When I became a nail technician, bright colours were my favourite way to express myself. Having a few different colours of this logo makes it flexible. I could use it anywhere, on anything!\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"317b19d\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"97ef3e7\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6b5de81\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/blackWname.png\",\"id\":108},\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"28e6c44\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b4b8858\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d6c3f24\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/whiteWname.png\",\"id\":118},\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"864b59c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f791950\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"43675b2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"editor\":\"<p>These other logo variations include my name underneath my symbol. I made this version for when I needed a more boxed in version of my logo - and needed my full name front and centre!\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"60d3eef\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"45ee879\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f1138be\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"The Process\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"66119a9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/img001.jpg\",\"id\":143},\"image_size\":\"full\",\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"fd405d3\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"45bb637\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9ea2b41\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/test.png\",\"id\":116},\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c162266\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"55f29af\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b044f29\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"editor\":\"<p>I went through a quick but thorough process to create this logo. I really had my mind set on what I wanted to portray in my logo and my brand.\\u00a0<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
