(1196, 253, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"30cdbb7\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b780a1d\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"037624d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Personal Logo\",\"title_color\":\"#a48179\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"700\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1879427c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b95864a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"351c252c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Since I was young, I have loved art, computers and space. I am enthralled by the way a brush and some colour can change the look and feel of something. I am astounded by the way you can create something from your mind with a little imagination and some supplies. I have been using a computer since the age of 5 and within a few months, I was teaching my parents how to do things on the computer. And I am completely taken aback by the vastness of space, and imagining what could be out there.<\\/p><p>So, with all these things in mind, a graphic designer seemed like the career that contained the perfect combination of my favourite things and my skill sets. But, where could I introduce some space vibes? Of course, every client wouldn\'t want NASA type logos or galaxy watercolored backgrounds and all that stuff.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>I decided that for my personal logo - I would create a nerdy, spacey, astronaut feel.\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Why not? It\'s my logo!<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a88138d\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"47f8e64\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"70555a3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"The Logo\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"dcf5532\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8888\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/12\\/black.png\",\"id\":105},\"link_to\":\"file\",\"open_lightbox\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"be05a77\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"23e1d26\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a3cd6e3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"editor\":\"<p>This is the basic logo. The logo that would be seen most of the time - you know, when some would say it\'s \\\"inappropriate\\\" to have a bright pink logo present. Which is strange... Because pink is a fantastically happy colour.<\\/p><p>I created this logo by finding a NASA-like font and making use of it to reflect me! I brought the letters A and W (no, not like the burgers, but yum!) into Illustrator and modified them until they melded into one another.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>It\'s funny, it kind of looks the way I sign my initials.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"672cbfe\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"9d319fc\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b95649e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"element