(1209, 254, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"30cdbb7\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b780a1d\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"037624d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Personal Logo\",\"title_color\":\"#a48179\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"700\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1879427c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b95864a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"351c252c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Since I was young, I have loved art, computers and space. I am enthralled by the way a brush and some colour can change the look and feel of something. I am astounded by the way you can create something from your mind with a little imagination and some supplies. I have been using a computer since the age of 5 and within a few months, I was teaching my parents how to do things on the computer. And I am completely taken aback by the vastness of space, and imagining what could be out there.<\\/p><p>So, with all these things in mind, a graphic designer seemed like the career that contained the perfect combination of my favourite things and my skill sets. But, where could I introduce some space vibes? Of course, every client wouldn\'t want NASA type logos or galaxy watercolored backgrounds and all that stuff.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>I decided that for my personal logo - I would create a nerdy, spacey, astronaut feel.\\u00a0<\\/p><p><span style=\\\"font-size: 1rem;\\\">Why not? It\'s my logo!<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a88138d\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"se