(13, 1, '2018-12-01 14:48:47', '2018-12-01 19:48:47', '<h2>Personal Logo</h2>\r\nSince I was young, I have loved art, computers and space. I am enthralled by the way a brush and some colour can change the look and feel of something. I am astounded by the way you can create something from your mind with a little imagination and some supplies. I have been using a computer since the age of 5 and within a few months, I was teaching my parents how to do things on the computer. And I am completely taken aback by the vastness of space, and imagining what could be out there.\r\n\r\nSo, with all these things in mind, a graphic designer seemed like the career that contained the perfect combination of my favourite things and my skill sets. But, where could I introduce some space vibes? Of course, every client wouldn\'t want NASA type logos or galaxy watercolored backgrounds and all that stuff.\r\n\r\nI decided that for my personal logo - I would create a nerdy, spacey, astronaut feel.\r\n\r\nWhy not? It\'s my logo!\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Black\" width=\"433\" height=\"432\" />\r\n\r\nThis is the basic logo. The logo that would be seen most of the time - you know, when some would say it\'s \"inappropriate\" to have a bright pink logo present. Which is strange... Because pink is a fantastically happy colour.\r\n\r\nI created this logo by finding a NASA-like font and making use of it to reflect me! I brought the letters A and W (no, not like the burgers, but yum!) into Illustrator and modified them until they melded into one another.\r\n\r\nIt\'s funny, it kind of looks the way I sign my initials.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWguides.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWguides.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWguides.png 1208w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWguides-300x221.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWguides-768x565.png 768w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWguides-1024x753.png 1024w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Black Clearspace\" width=\"1208\" height=\"888\" /> </a>\r\n<h2>Logo Variations</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Blue\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellow.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellow.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellow.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellow-300x296.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellow-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Yellow\" width=\"433\" height=\"427\" /> </a>\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pink.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pink.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pink-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pink-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pink-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Pink\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" />\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Green\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Blue Outline\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Yellow Outline\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Pink Outline\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Green Outline\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n\r\nThese are all the variations of my personal logo. There is not much difference from the basic logo - but I have always been drawn to bright and vibrant colour. When I became a nail technician, bright colours were my favourite way to express myself. Having a few different colours of this logo makes it flexible. I could use it anywhere, on anything!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname.png 721w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Black Square With Name\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname.png 721w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - White Square With Name\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /> </a>\r\n\r\nThese other logo variations include my name underneath my symbol. I made this version for when I needed a more boxed in version of my logo - and needed my full name front and centre!\r\n<h2>The Process</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001.jpg 2483w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001-231x300.jpg 231w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001-768x998.jpg 768w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001-788x1024.jpg 788w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Process Sketches\" width=\"2483\" height=\"3228\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis Logo - Process Illustrator\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n\r\nI went through a quick but thorough process to create this logo. I really had my mind set on what I wanted to portray in my logo and my brand.', 'Personal Logo', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'awlogo', '', '', '2018-12-13 16:47:16', '2018-12-13 21:47:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?p=13', 3, 'post', '', 0),
(14, 1, '2018-12-01 14:48:47', '2018-12-01 19:48:47', 'I was blessed with a very steady hand; and it comes in very handy when you\'re doing these little delicate things. Nature is so fantastic, enjoy it. Let it make you happy. I like to beat the brush. Do an almighty painting with us. That\'s a son of a gun of a cloud. Everybody\'s different. Trees are different. Let them all be individuals.\r\n\r\nThis present moment is perfect simply due to the fact you\'re experiencing it. This is your world. Let\'s get wild today. Don\'t be bashful drop me a line.\r\n\r\nYou want your tree to have some character. Make it special. God gave you this gift of imagination. Use it. I want everbody to be happy. That\'s what it\'s all about. I\'m a water fanatic. I love water. Now let\'s put some happy little clouds in here.', 'Test 3', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-01 14:48:47', '2018-12-01 19:48:47', '', 13, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/12/01/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(16, 1, '2018-12-01 15:14:49', '2018-12-01 20:14:49', '<h2>Who we are</h2><p>Our website address is: http://localhost:8888.</p><h2>What personal data we collect and why we collect it</h2><h3>Comments</h3><p>When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor&#8217;s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.</p><p>An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.</p><h3>Media</h3><p>If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.</p><h3>Contact forms</h3><h3>Cookies</h3><p>If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.</p><p>If you have an account and you log in to this site, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.</p><p>When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select &quot;Remember Me&quot;, your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.</p><p>If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.</p><h3>Embedded content from other websites</h3><p>Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.</p><p>These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.</p><h3>Analytics</h3><h2>Who we share your data with</h2><h2>How long we retain your data</h2><p>If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.</p><p>For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.</p><h2>What rights you have over your data</h2><p>If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.</p><h2>Where we send your data</h2><p>Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.</p><h2>Your contact information</h2><h2>Additional information</h2><h3>How we protect your data</h3><h3>What data breach procedures we have in place</h3><h3>What third parties we receive data from</h3><h3>What automated decision making and/or profiling we do with user data</h3><h3>Industry regulatory disclosure requirements</h3>', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-01 15:14:49', '2018-12-01 20:14:49', '', 3, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/12/01/3-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
