(19, 1, '2018-12-01 15:15:02', '2018-12-01 20:15:02', '<h2>Hello!</h2>\r\nMy name is Alyssa. Pronounced uh-li-ss-uh. Not Alysha. Not Melissa. Sometimes you can get away with calling me Aly. But my name is Alyssa. Last name, Willis. I have heard so many \"What you talkin\' \'bout Willis\" jokes in my life, I will not laugh if you attempt it. Stop that. Get some help.\r\n\r\nI am a student at North Island College in Comox Valley studying in the Communication Design Program. Since I was a child, I have had a love for art and computers. I first explored my love of art through the basic paint and pens. Later on in life, I became a certified Nail Technician. I find my Nail Technician training really helped me with my art skills, my colour theory and my tactful and caring nature with clients.\r\n\r\nSince enrolling in the Communication Design Program, I feel as though I have found my calling in life. And although I am still learning, I am so proud of my skill set thus far.\r\n\r\nI am a lifelong and <strong><em>die-hard</em></strong> Disney/Pixar fan. I am the reigning champ of \"Name That Tune: Disney Edition\" in my family/friend group. I carry that title with pride. I worked hard for that, man.\r\n\r\nMy other interests include: Vines and Vine references, Youtube, photography, Starbucks, comedy and horror/thriller movies, the vastness of space, conspiracy theories, Reddit, nail art, 90\'s cartoons and movies, thrift shopping, and cats. Especially my fur baby, Mew. And Wilfred Warrior on Instagram.\r\n\r\nI hope to travel one day, and have a list of places that I would love to explore, including: Disneyland (again), Peru, Scotland and the Philippines.\r\n\r\nI am almost always smiling and laughing, or finding a way to make others smile and laugh because I think that is what life is all about. In the end, it\'s about the memories we make.\r\n\r\nI would love to help people create their brand, develop their brand\'s personality and bring it to life. If you are in the process of getting your brand on it\'s feet, I would love to help enable you to express yourself.\r\n<h3>Skill Set</h3>\r\nILLUSTRATOR\r\n<i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i> 5/5\r\nPHOTOSHOP\r\n<i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i> 4/5\r\nINDESIGN\r\n<i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i> 4.5/5\r\nHTML 5\r\n<i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i> 3.5/5\r\nCSS\r\n<i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i> 3.5/5\r\nPHP\r\n<i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i> 1/5\r\nJAVASCRIPT\r\n<i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i> 1/5\r\nDISNEY FACTS\r\n<i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i> 5/5\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721.jpg 1483w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721-300x229.jpg 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721-768x585.jpg 768w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721-1024x780.jpg 1024w\" alt=\"Alyssa Willis\" width=\"1483\" height=\"1130\" /> </a>', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2018-12-13 17:05:25', '2018-12-13 22:05:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=19', 1, 'page', '', 0),
