(25, 1, '2018-12-01 15:32:00', '2018-12-01 20:32:00', 'If there\'s two big trees invariably sooner or later there\'s gonna be a little tree. Those great big fluffy clouds. Everybody needs a friend. We don\'t have anything but happy trees here. We tell people sometimes: we\'re like drug dealers, come into town and get everybody absolutely addicted to painting. It doesn\'t take much to get you addicted. In your world you can create anything you desire.\r\n\r\nAnd that\'s when it becomes fun - you don\'t have to spend your time thinking about what\'s happening - you just let it happen. Now we can begin working on lots of happy little things. If what you\'re doing doesn\'t make you happy - you\'re doing the wrong thing. The shadows are just like the highlights, but we\'re going in the opposite direction.\r\n\r\nIn life you need colors. This is a fantastic little painting. All you need is a dream in your heart, and an almighty knife. This is your world.', 'Visual Identity: Espress Yourself', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-01 15:32:00', '2018-12-01 20:32:00', '', 9, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/12/01/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(26, 1, '2018-12-01 15:32:31', '2018-12-01 20:32:31', 'You need the dark in order to show the light. There isn\'t a rule. You just practice and find out which way works best for you. And I will hypnotize that just a little bit. Let\'s get wild today. All kinds of happy little splashes. Talent is a pursued interest. That is to say, anything you practice you can do.\r\n\r\nDon\'t forget to tell these special people in your life just how special they are to you. And right there you got an almighty cloud. Trees grow however makes them happy. Maybe there\'s a happy little waterfall happening over here. Exercising the imagination, experimenting with talents, being creative; these things, to me, are truly the windows to your soul.\r\n\r\nIt looks so good, I might as well not stop. There are no limits in this world. Nature is so fantastic, enjoy it. Let it make you happy. Work that paint. Didn\'t you know you had that much power? You can move mountains. You can do anything.', 'Re-Branding Project: True Blue Pet Supplies', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-01 15:32:31', '2018-12-01 20:32:31', '', 11, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/12/01/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(27, 1, '2018-12-01 15:36:54', '2018-12-01 20:36:54', 'I was blessed with a very steady hand; and it comes in very handy when you\'re doing these little delicate things. Nature is so fantastic, enjoy it. Let it make you happy. I like to beat the brush. Do an almighty painting with us. That\'s a son of a gun of a cloud. Everybody\'s different. Trees are different. Let them all be individuals.\r\n\r\nThis present moment is perfect simply due to the fact you\'re experiencing it. This is your world. Let\'s get wild today. Don\'t be bashful drop me a line.\r\n\r\nYou want your tree to have some character. Make it special. God gave you this gift of imagination. Use it. I want everbody to be happy. That\'s what it\'s all about. I\'m a water fanatic. I love water. Now let\'s put some happy little clouds in here.', 'THIRD PROJECT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-01 15:36:54', '2018-12-01 20:36:54', '', 13, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/12/01/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
