(151, 1, '2018-12-06 19:12:24', '2018-12-07 00:12:24', '<h2>Personal Logo</h2>		\n		I was blessed with a very steady hand; and it comes in very handy when you\'re doing these little delicate things. Nature is so fantastic, enjoy it. Let it make you happy. I like to beat the brush. Do an almighty painting with us. That\'s a son of a gun of a cloud. Everybody\'s different. Trees are different. Let them all be individuals.\nThis present moment is perfect simply due to the fact you\'re experiencing it. This is your world. Let\'s get wild today. Don\'t be bashful drop me a line.\nYou want your tree to have some character. Make it special. God gave you this gift of imagination. Use it. I want everbody to be happy. That\'s what it\'s all about. I\'m a water fanatic. I love water. Now let\'s put some happy little clouds in here.		\n			<h2>The Logo</h2>		\n										<img width=\"433\" height=\"432\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n		Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.		\n			<h2>Logo Variations</h2>		\n										<img width=\"433\" height=\"433\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n										<img width=\"433\" height=\"427\" src=\"http