(163, 1, '2018-12-06 19:47:24', '2018-12-07 00:47:24', '<h2>Visual Brand Identity Project</h2>		\n		If there\'s two big trees invariably sooner or later there\'s gonna be a little tree. Those great big fluffy clouds. Everybody needs a friend. We don\'t have anything but happy trees here. We tell people sometimes: we\'re like drug dealers, come into town and get everybody absolutely addicted to painting. It doesn\'t take much to get you addicted. In your world you can create anything you desire.\nAnd that\'s when it becomes fun - you don\'t have to spend your time thinking about what\'s happening - you just let it happen. Now we can begin working on lots of happy little things. If what you\'re doing doesn\'t make you happy - you\'re doing the wrong thing. The shadows are just like the highlights, but we\'re going in the opposite direction.\nIn life you need colors. This is a fantastic little painting. All you need is a dream in your heart, and an almighty knife. This is your world.		\n			<h2>The Logo</h2>		\n		Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.		\n										<img width=\"525\" height=\"205\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/BIGCOLOURED-1024x399.png\" alt=\"Espress Yourself Logo\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/BIGCOLOURED-1024x399.png 1024w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/BIGCOLOURED-300x117.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/BIGCOLOURED-768x299.png 768w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/BIGCOLOURED.png 1303w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n										<img width=\"525\" height=\"168\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/BIGNOCOLOUR-1024x328.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/BIGNOCOLOUR-1024x328.png 1024w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/BIGNOCOLOUR-300x96.png 30