tline-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />								</a>\n											<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\n							<img width=\"433\" height=\"433\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />								</a>\n		<p>These are all the variations of my personal logo. There is not much difference from the basic logo - but I have always been drawn to bright and vibrant colour. When I became a nail technician, bright colours were my favourite way to express myself. Having a few different colours of this logo makes it flexible. I could use it anywhere, on anything! </p>		\n											<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\n							<img width=\"525\" height=\"525\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname.png 721w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />								</a>\n											<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\n							<img width=\"525\" height=\"525\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname.png 721w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />								</a>\n		<p>These other logo variations include my name underneath my symbol. I made this version for when I needed a more boxed in version of my logo - and needed my full name front and centre! </p>		\n			<h2>The Process</h2>		\n											<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\n							<img width=\"2483\" height=\"3228\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001.jpg 2483w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001-231x300.jpg 231w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001-768x998.jpg 768w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001-788x1024.jpg 788w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />								</a>\n											<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\n							<img width=\"433\" height=\"433\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />								</a>\n		<p>I went through a quick but thorough process to create this logo. I really had my mind set on what I wanted to portray in my logo and my brand. </p>', 'Personal Logo', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-07 23:32:00', '2018-12-08 04:32:00', '', 13, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/12/07/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
