(235, 1, '2018-12-07 23:57:04', '2018-12-08 04:57:04', '<h5>Documentation</h5>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5>November 12/18</h5>\r\n• Created portfolio website\r\n• Added .htaccess &amp; .gitignore files\r\n• Created child theme for 2017\r\n• Modified CSS\r\n• Created pages &amp; posts\r\n<h5>December 1/18</h5>\r\n• Template modifications: enable debugging, removed powered by Wordpress footer message, modified CSS, composition changes\r\n• Custom sidebar: about page\r\n• Added Elementor, Intuitive Custom Post Order, Metaslider/Lightbox Plugins\r\n<h5>December 2/18</h5>\r\n• Created templates for content and images in Elementor for each post page\r\n• Added images to Rebranding post\r\n• Added images to Personal Logo post\r\n• Added contact form on Contact page\r\n<h5>December 3/18</h5>\r\n• Added headings\r\n• Changed colour of headings\r\n• Changed colour/typeface of headings and body copy in posts\r\n• Removed post content from appearing on post page\r\n• Changed Portfolio page to the front page\r\n<h5>December 6/18</h5>\r\n• Added images to Visual Identity post\r\n• Changed header image on site\r\n• Changed paragraph and header colours to match new header image\r\n• Added information to Contact page\r\n<h5>December 7/18</h5>\r\n• Modified style.css to change text colour of paragraphs\r\n• Added content to Rebranding &amp; Visual Identity posts\r\n• Began adding content to Personal Logo post\r\n• Modified functions.php: added obscure login errors &amp; added custom login logo\r\n• Modified CSS: changed main navigation link colour and hover colour\r\n• Added home page back to main menu\r\n• Added content to home page\r\n• Added posts as drop down menu on portfolio link on main menu\r\n• Added more content to Personal Logo post\r\n•  Updated About page with skills (stars) and moved elements around using Elementor', 'Documentation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '65-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-07 23:57:04', '2018-12-08 04:57:04', '', 65, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/12