(237, 1, '2018-12-08 00:32:48', '2018-12-08 05:32:48', '<img width=\"525\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721-1024x780.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721-1024x780.jpg 1024w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721-300x229.jpg 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721-768x585.jpg 768w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_3721.jpg 1483w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n			<h2>Alyssa Willis</h2>		\n		<p>Hi! My name is Alyssa. Pronounced uh-li-ss-uh. Not Alysha. Not Melissa. Sometimes you can get away with calling me Aly. But my name is Alyssa. Last name, Willis. I have heard so many \"What you talkin\' \'bout Willis\" jokes in my life, I will not laugh if you attempt it. Stop that. Get some help.</p><p>I am a student at North Island College in Comox Valley studying in the Communication Design Program. Since I was a child, I have had a love for art and computers. I first explored my love of art through the basic paint and pens. Later on in life, I became a certified Nail Technician. I find my Nail Technician training really helped me with my art skills, my colour theory and my tactful and caring nature with clients.</p><p>Since enrolling in the Communication Design Program, I feel as though I have found my calling in life. And although I am still learning, I am so proud of my skill set thus far. </p><p>I am a lifelong and <strong><em>die-hard</em></strong> Disney/Pixar fan. I am the reigning champ of \"Name That Tune: Disney Edition\" in my family/friend group. I carry that title with pride. I worked hard for that, man.</p><p>My other interests include: Vines and Vine references, Youtube, photography, Starbucks, comedy and horror/thriller movies, the vastness of space, conspiracy theories, Reddit, nail art, 90\'s cartoons and movies, thrift shopping, and cats. Especially my fur baby, Mew. And Wilfred Warrior on Instagram.</p><p>I hope to travel one day, and have a list of places that I would love to explore, including: Disneyland (again), Peru, Scotland and the Philippines. </p><p>I am almost always smiling and laughing, or finding a way to make others smile and laugh because I think that is what life is all about. In the end, it\'s about the memories we make. </p><p>I would love to help people create their brand, develop their brand\'s personality and bring it to life. If you are in the process of getting your brand on it\'s feet, I would love to help enable you to express yourself. </p><p> </p>		\n			<h3>Skill Set</h3>		\n							ILLUSTRATOR\n						<i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i> 5/5		\n							PHOTOSHOP\n						<i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i> 4/5		\n							INDESIGN\n						<i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i> 4.5/5		\n							HTML 5\n						<i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i> 3.5/5		\n							CSS\n						<i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i> 3.5/5		\n							PHP\n						<i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i> 1/5		\n							JAVASCRIPT\n						<i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i> 1/5		\n							DISNEY FACTS\n						<i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i><i>&#61446;</i> 5/5', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-08 00:32:48', '2018-12-08 05:32:48', '', 19, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/12/08/19-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
