(250, 1, '2018-12-08 16:16:10', '2018-12-08 21:16:10', '<h2>Personal Logo</h2>\r\nSince I was young, I have loved art, computers and space. I am enthralled by the way a brush and some colour can change the look and feel of something. I am astounded by the way you can create something from your mind with a little imagination and some supplies. I have been using a computer since the age of 5 and within a few months, I was teaching my parents how to do things on the computer. And I am completely taken aback by the vastness of space, and imagining what could be out there.\r\n\r\nSo, with all these things in mind, a graphic designer seemed like the career that contained the perfect combination of my favourite things and my skill sets. But, where could I introduce some space vibes? Of course, every client wouldn\'t want NASA type logos or galaxy watercolored backgrounds and all that stuff.\r\n\r\nI decided that for my personal logo - I would create a nerdy, spacey, astronaut feel.\r\n\r\nWhy not? It\'s my logo!\r\n<h2>The Logo</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/black-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"432\" /> </a>\r\n\r\nThis is the basic logo. The logo that would be seen most of the time - you know, when some would say it\'s \"inappropriate\" to have a bright pink logo present. Which is strange... Because pink is a fantastically happy colour.\r\n\r\nI created this logo by finding a NASA-like font and making use of it to reflect me! I brought the letters A and W (no, not like the burgers, but yum!) into Illustrator and modified them until they melded into one another.\r\n\r\nIt\'s funny, it kind of looks the way I sign my initials.\r\n<h2>Logo Variations</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blue-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellow.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellow.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellow.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellow-300x296.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellow-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"427\" /> </a>\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pink.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pink.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pink-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pink-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pink-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" />\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/green-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blueoutline-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/yellowoutline-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/pinkoutline-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/greenoutline-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n\r\nThese are all the variations of my personal logo. There is not much difference from the basic logo - but I have always been drawn to bright and vibrant colour. When I became a nail technician, bright colours were my favourite way to express myself. Having a few different colours of this logo makes it flexible. I could use it anywhere, on anything!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname.png 721w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/blackWname-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname.png 721w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/whiteWname-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /> </a>\r\n\r\nThese other logo variations include my name underneath my symbol. I made this version for when I needed a more boxed in version of my logo - and needed my full name front and centre!\r\n<h2>The Process</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001.jpg 2483w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001-231x300.jpg 231w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001-768x998.jpg 768w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img001-788x1024.jpg 788w\" alt=\"\" width=\"2483\" height=\"3228\" /> </a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\">\r\n<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test.png 433w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test-150x150.png 150w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/test-100x100.png 100w\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"433\" /> </a>\r\n\r\nI went through a quick but thorough process to create this logo. I really had my mind set on what I wanted to portray in my logo and my brand.', 'Personal Logo', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-08 16:16:10', '2018-12-08 21:16:10', '', 13, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/12/08/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
