8/12/test-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />								</a>\n		<p>I went through a quick but thorough process to create this logo. I really had my mind set on what I wanted to portray in my logo and my brand. </p>', 'Personal Logo', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-08 16:32:54', '2018-12-08 21:32:54', '', 13, 'http://localhost:8888/2018/12/08/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
